[December 11th, 2020 3:50 PM] mose: &gt; GitHub Actions hosted runners for macOS may experience longer wait times during the week of December 14.
&gt; 
&gt; During the week of December 14-18, GitHub will be performing scheduled maintenance on one of our datacenters that may result in longer than normal wait times for GitHub-hosted macOS runners: macos-latest, macos-10.14, or macos-10.15. In some cases, it may be possible that jobs will time out or be cancelled, and will need to be restarted.

